          "Avoid opening suspicious attachments.",
          "Enable multi-factor authentication.",
          "Update your email application regularly."
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "FAQ",
        "content": [
          {
            "question": "I cannot send emails.",
            "answer": "Verify your internet connection, mailbox quota, and SMTP settings."
          },
          {
            "question": "Why am I not receiving emails?",
            "answer": "Check your spam folder, mailbox storage, and synchronization status."
          },
          {
            "question": "Outlook keeps asking for my password.",
            "answer": "Verify your credentials or contact IT to reset your account."
          }
